descriptionHtml:
[center][size=4]Norine is one of my presets.[/size]

[size=4]She will be used as an upcoming Follower, the author of the follower will be announced later.[/size]

[size=4]To make Norine appear as in the images you will need the following mods.

Race : Nord[/size]
[size=4]True Eyes : Human Grey Nebula[/size]
[size=4]KS Hairdos : HDT 1Sky250[/size]
[size=4]Demoniac Skin Texture[/size]
[size=4]Brow : vanilla skyrim human 1

[/size][size=5]Installation:
[/size][size=4]Drop the .jslot file into your SKSE/pluggins/Chargen/Presets folder[/size]

[size=2]Credits

[/size]True eyes
KS Hairdos HDT
Demoniac Skin Texture[/center]
